    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single shortfall in Test conditions (achieved 2, required 3) is accepted based on the explicitly scoped COU limited to static compression-bending, corroborating published literature, and the conservative acceptance thresholds applied to output comparison metrics. All quantitative acceptance criteria (E/uval < 1.96, percent difference < 10%) are satisfied for all three QoIs. The package is submitted under ProfileMinimal; digital signature is pending completion of the institutional signature workflow and will be appended prior to regulatory submission.",
